name: Wing
content:
Wing was a human male who lived in the city of Calodan on the planet of Corvus, the city was ruled by the ruthless Magistrate Morgan Elsbeth, who had promised Mandalorian Bounty hunter Din Djarin a pure beskar spear if he killed Ahsoka Tano.
However, Tano and Djarin teamed up and overthrew Morgan Elsbeth's rule of Calodan, giving Wing the Governorship of Calodan.
Wing debuted in "Chapter 13: The Jedi" from the second season of the television series The Mandalorian, which was written and directed by Dave Filoni and released on Disney+ on November 27, 2020. Credited as "Governor Wing," he was played by Wing Tao Chao, an architect and Disney Legend from Walt Disney Imagineering.
